# Introduction to Bayesian Statistics
## Second Edition
### William M. Bolstad
### 2007, John Wiley and Sons Inc.

This site hosts supplementary materials for the text. Please note that the R pacakge `Bolstad` is **not** hosted here. The latest version can be found on [CRAN](https://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/Bolstad/), however it is most easily installed by typing the following in R
```{r}
install.packages("Bolstad")
```


All queries should be directed to James Curran <j.curran@auckland.ac.nz>

